<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wave-v">wave <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /weɪv/    美 /wev/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>摇摆：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The branches were waving in the breeze.
树枝在微风中摇曳。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>挥舞；挥动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Crowds lined the route, <strong>waving flags</strong> and cheering.
人群沿路排成行，又是挥旗，又是欢呼。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>挥手 (表示...)；(向...) 挥手示意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>wave sb goodbye</strong> / <strong>wave goodbye to sb</strong>
向某人挥手道别</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He waved until they were out of sight.
他向他们挥手，直到看不见他们为止。</p></div></div>